Package: sunits
Type: Package
Title: Simple Vector with Value and Units
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jameel Alsalam
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: If you commonly find yourself carrying dual `unit` and `value`
    columns, then this package presents an alternative s3 vctrs class
    which carries them together. Allows easy transformation back and forth
    from a dataframe column. Implemented via `vctrs::rcrd` class.
